{
  "stem": "7683.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I figured that gives me-- a farmer, that gives me food, shelter.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And a matter of fact, I could even help my pa-- my father, because you got so much paid in form of corn and things like that.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I could sell it, and I could help him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "What was a really big help for them, too, and for myself.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And-- and then my brother went to work there, too-- with another farmer.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And also a friend what has-- has worked there, also farmer.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we-- for about two years, I worked there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I did all the work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was young, and enthusiastic about work.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So-- and-- and you know, what else can you expect?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I worked there for two years, and I did all kinds of-- but of course, a Ukrainian.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "By Ukrainian, I worked there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They was very nice people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They treated me nice.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Had nothing to complain on that, till there came an order that Jews cannot work anymore in the-- any farm there.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And all the Jews which worked there has-- have to come to the nearest biggest city.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, in that time already, my father and his wife, my stepmother, they were sent away already.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was-- they took-- at that time, they took only the older ones.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my-- they were sent away, and I didn't know where they went to.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and-- and-- and as I say, when there came the order, that we-- all the Jews had to go to the nearest biggest city.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So my brother and myself and a friend what worked also the farmer decided not to go to the city because we expect it could be very bad for us.",
      "word_count": 30
    }
  ],
